============
Description:
============

This is a mod for Minetest-c55.

Adds 2 limestone blocks and lime for crafting.

There are 2 blocks for building. One based on sand, the other from desert sand.
They generate where ever there is sand and water.

Lime is found in stone and desert stone and uses the familar mineral pattern for identification.


==============
Dependancies:
==============

See depends.txt file.



=========
Recipes:
=========

Limestone blocks:
-----------------

1. sand / desert sand
2. sand / desert sand
4. lime 
5. lime 

Produces 1 limestone block depending on the sand type used.

